---
<section class="relative pt-44 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-[#FFF0F5]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-12">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6">
          Nutrición <span class="italic text-[#D81B60]">consciente</span> para una vida plena.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
          Transforma tu relación con la comida mediante un enfoque especializado y personalizado que se adapta a tu estilo de vida.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#services" class="bg-[#D81B60] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-center hover:bg-[#B3154C] transition-all shadow-xl shadow-pink-100">
            Descubre nuestros servicios
          </a>
          <a href="#about" class="border-2 border-[#FF6B9B] text-[#D81B60] px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-center hover:bg-pink-50 transition-all">
            Conoce más
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <div class="flex -space-x-2">
            {[1,2,3,4].map(() => (
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white bg-pink-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-[10px] text-pink-600">❤</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <span>+500 vidas transformadas este año</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 relative">
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl skew-y-1 transform group hover:skew-y-0 transition-transform duration-700">
          <img 
            src="/assets/hands-strawberries.jpg" 
            alt="Fresa en manos - Nutrición Natural" 
            class="w-full h-[600px] object-cover scale-110 group-hover:scale-100 transition-transform duration-700"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-pink-600/10 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative elements -->
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-pink-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-48 h-48 bg-[#FFD1DC] rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
